				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2c38e4c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="2c38e4c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p>We have not fixed prices as this depends on the extent of the project and features that customers request. Our rates are affordable and that is for sure you will get the most upon your investment. Contact us for a free quote based on your web design project needs. ZAMAN IT <strong>Best web design company in Bangladesh.</strong></p>						</div>
				</div>
