				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Website Management Training for Our Clients?</h2>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b6e481c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b6e481c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p>As a leading best web design company in Bangladesh, we offer a dedicated training session to help our clients manage their websites independently. While we don’t provide full web training courses, our tailored session equips customers with essential skills to confidently <strong>update and maintain</strong> their sites.</p>						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c899ea3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="c899ea3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">How much does your website cost?</h2>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-de6d3ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="de6d3ce" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p>ZAMAN IT, we are committed to offering affordable and high-quality web design services, making us the best web design company in Bangladesh. We have several packages tailored to meet various needs. Our basic business website package starts at only <strong>TK 15,000</strong>, which includes a 5-page web design ideal for small to medium businesses. We also provide specialized packages for e-commerce and newspaper websites. For a full overview of our offerings, please visit the Services section on our website.</p>						</div>
